  "title": "日常漫步 Vol.19 之稻田与猫",
  "summary": "距离上次到老屋咖啡5个月了，今天计划去溜达下，在村口遇到村里在办“那溪稻香生活节”，还有研学活动，吸引来不少人 […]",
  "content": "<p>距离<a href=\"https://yayu.net/5268.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">上次到老屋咖啡</a>5个月了，今天计划去溜达下，在村口遇到村里在办“那溪稻香生活节”，还有研学活动，吸引来不少人。村里大改造，菜田换了金黄的稻田，水塘边还有有挖掘机在吭哧吭哧的工作着，下次再来，应该又会多不少趣味。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/202511231340045.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/2025112313393694.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/2025112313400447.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\"></p>\n<p>上回来猫宝宝刚出生，几个月过去已经分不出哪个是猫妈哪个是猫宝。店里已经有6只猫，足够撸个过瘾了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/20251123133950100.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/2025112313400548.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/2025112313400562.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/2025112313400674.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/2025112313400632.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/202511231340079-1.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/2025112313401087.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/2025112313400879.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/2025112313401090.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/2025112313394396.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/202511231340079.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/2025112313400944.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/2025112313400975.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/2025112313400830.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/202511231340085.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/2025112313400574.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/2025112313401176.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\"></p>\n<p>By 理光 GR3</p>\n<p>拍摄地点：珠海市那洲村</p>",
